who want more female CEOs of color and more disabled transgender drone pilots,

17:28.660 --> 17:32.660
while the activists accuse the Marxists of being a boys' club of brochelists,

17:32.660 --> 17:36.580
no more woke on gender and race issues than the average Jordan Peterson fan.

17:36.580 --> 17:42.020
