22:58.900 --> 23:03.540
Let us remind you that nature has so made the lobster

23:03.540 --> 23:07.060
that some individuals be stronger than the others.

23:07.060 --> 23:15.060
Therefore, let not the power of our crustacean sovereignty be anywise impugned.

23:15.060 --> 23:21.460
And as for parliamentarians, well, let them vote for cake.

23:24.180 --> 23:24.980
Very good.

23:24.980 --> 23:25.540
Thank you.

