23:34.180 --> 23:37.220
of postmodern neo-Marxism as the supervillain

23:37.220 --> 23:40.020
in a childishly simple worldview he's promoting

23:40.020 --> 23:43.140
where these evil leftists are out to destroy the West.

23:43.140 --> 23:45.860
Now it's time to inspect the other side of this coin.

23:45.860 --> 23:48.340
What, exactly, is the West?

23:48.340 --> 23:51.140
Well, there's an academic usage of the term the West

23:51.140 --> 23:52.980
that describes the intellectual tradition

23:52.980 --> 23:56.740
that runs from ancient Athens to modern-day Europe and its colonies.

23:56.740 --> 24:01.060
