24:01.060 --> 24:05.300
and show how the very idea is racist and exclusionary and supremacist

24:05.300 --> 24:08.420
and justifies imperialism and all that kind of thing.

24:08.420 --> 24:10.180
But we don't have time for that right now.

24:10.180 --> 24:12.420
So I'm just going to grant that the West is a thing

24:12.420 --> 24:14.660
and look at how Jordan Peterson thinks about it.

24:14.660 --> 24:17.860
For Peterson, the West seems to be equivalent to capitalism,

24:17.860 --> 24:21.940
individualism, the idea that each human has a spark of divinity

24:22.020 --> 24:25.220
and he therefore equates it with Judeo-Christian values,

24:25.220 --> 24:29.700
a term more popular with conservative pundits than intellectual historians.

24:29.700 --> 24:34.100
Peterson contrasts Judeo-Christian values with postmodern neo-Marxism,

24:34.100 --> 24:39.140
which he describes as anti-Western, collectivist, relativist, and totalitarian.

24:39.140 --> 24:43.220
This framing of a conflict of ideas in terms of geographical chauvinism

24:43.220 --> 24:46.580
and external threat is inaccurate and scaremongering.

24:46.580 --> 24:48.820
Marxism is Western philosophy.

24:48.820 --> 24:51.140
